title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H3 - Nov 13 2021
itunes:title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H3 - Nov 13 2021
description:
Bill O'Reilly talks with Clay and Buck about Biden's dismal performance and Bill's upcoming history tour with President Trump: "I'm not doing the history tour for any other reason than to inform the American people on what really happened during those four years of Trump because nobody knows what happened because it was never reported honestly." The latest on the Kyle Rittenhouse trial. C&B take calls on the Rittenhouse trial.
